 25.4844C67.4779 20.8918 71.3247 17.0745 75.9173 17.0745ZM75.8552 30.7932C78.718 30.7932 80.9545 28.4372 80.9545 25.4852C80.9545 22.5626 78.718 20.2066 75.8552 20.2066C72.9621 20.2066 70.7559 22.5331 70.7559 25.4852C70.7559 28.4077 72.9621 30.7932 75.8552 30.7932ZM86.4714 17.523H89.6027V20.5348H89.6624C90.7365 18.6226 92.2567 17.0753 94.941 17.0753C98.4301 17.0753 100.338 19.6998 100.338 23.3976V33.4768H96.9122V23.9338C96.9122 21.7571 96.1075 20.1165 93.9642 20.1165C91.2799 20.1165 89.9078 22.7411 89.9078 25.2158V33.4768H86.4817L86.4714 17.523ZM110.037 24.1721H113.168V23.1586C113.168 21.518 112.184 20.2655 110.245 20.2655C108.397 20.2655 106.727 21.5483 105.892 23.3673L102.999 21.9658C104.341 18.8935 107.055 17.1342 110.276 17.1342C113.941 17.1342 116.598 19.2855 116.598 23.1586V30.1367C116.598 30.4945 116.658 30.6434 117.045 30.6434H118.24V33.4768H116.063C114.691 33.4768 113.767 32.6712 113.767 30.9414V30.1662H113.618C112.544 32.4928 110.367 33.8313 107.951 33.8313C105.387 33.8313 102.972 32.3406 102.972 29.2101C102.972 26.0795 106.014 24.1697 110.039 24.1697L110.037 24.1721ZM108.637 30.9988C110.789 30.9988 112.902 29.2101 113.17 26.5552H110.222C107.986 26.5552 106.405 27.3608 106.405 29.0005C106.405 30.253 107.329 30.9988 108.641 30.9988H108.637ZM120.63 11.5576H124.056V30.0467C124.056 30.4642 124.085 30.6434 124.592 30.6434H126.743V33.4768H123.422C121.245 33.4768 120.619 32.0752 120.619 30.0769L120.63 11.5576Z" fill="#00B7FF"/>
